  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="wrap split">
      <div>
        <h2>Solo worlds first. Local co-op when you are ready.</h2>
        <ul class="fact-list">
          <li>Worlds are bounded in size for reliable Quest performance, with seed-based generation so each world is unique.</li>
          <li>LAN multiplayer is host-authoritative and designed for local co-op sessions.</li>
          <li>Voice uses Meta Quest party chat; Blockiverse VR does not use in-app voice chat.</li>
          <li>World saves, inventory, comfort settings, and diagnostics stay local unless you choose to share them.</li>
        </ul>
